<LI>Borka Vranes, pensioner
<LI>Nada Vranes
<LI>Mica Vranes, Nada's husband
<LI>Nedeljko Igric, clerk
<LI>Nikola Stojanovic, pensioner
<LI>Nikola Niscevic, guard in prison
<LI>Marija Niscevic, his wife
