The continuation of the series of feuilletons about the history of psychodelic
revolution.  Albert Hofmann, LSD beginnings in 1943. in Switzerland. Than came
Ken Kesey, Pranksters, Greateful Dead, Timothy Leary, his book; "The
Psychodelic Experience", acidheads, deadheads. Californian Ethnopharmacist
Terence McKenna,who has researched "magic mushrooms" and plants in South
America, and developed a theory of neo-shamanism.<P>

