Rock, punk and its connection with the political scene in the world, mostly
oriented to the left wing.: Oasis, Pulp, Black Grape.
Blur and Simple Red included ib the runing campaign of Tony Blair and Labor
party. But the message is: "Labour is only minor evil than Torry".<P>

page: 35 - SLO-MOTION<P>
authors: ROBERT VALKAJ & BORIS POPOVIC<P>
24 hours of counter-stream rock and roll in Ljubljana, in one atomic shelter
in Gerbiceva (street), called Bunker "B- 51".<P>

page: 36 - HARD CORE SHOW OF "COWS" IN ZAGREB
            (Ruziona !!!)<P>
author: TIHANA KORAC & ALEKSANDRA VRANJES<P>
The concert of "Cows" in Zagreb's rock club "Jabuka", on their "Old Gold"
