unforgettable one hour and a half of the frenetic, noiseistic, expressionistic
dissipation.
<P>
page: 37 - A TRIUMPH OF WILL
            (Trijumf volje)<P>author: PEDRO GARMOBONZIA<P>
The Croatian fanzine comics scene. Most of them have only Xerox machine, a
little money and a lot of talent. "Endem" and "Vitez" (fanzines)
try to be shaped like the reviews of the "above ground" comics. "Variete
Radikal" pretends to be "under'alter art".
"Stripoholic" is dedicated to anarcho-punkers. "Katakomba" is a cemetery of
non- commercial comics.
They are all in the progressive phase, and there are also the announcement of
new ones: "Pirat", "Smack", and "Mrgud".<P>

