<HEAD>
<TITLE>refpic9</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="pictures/frback.jpg">

<HR>
<IMG SRC="pictures/refpic9.gif">
<P>

<STRONG><FONT SIZE="+2">This is really a big shame for Europe, for the whole world.  We believed in Europe, that this couldn't happen... this is honest Serbian people;  we defended ourselves for four years, we were afraid of their government, leaders and the people [Croatians]<BR> That's our destiny, I don't know why...  We have scattered, friends and relatives...  The hardest was to leave your birth place, churches, schools...  This is a terrible misfortune and suffering.  To bomb the refugees.  I heard stories like that as a child, but such suffering...  This is terrible.  They accepted us here, but that's not it.  A home town is the dearest thing in the world...<br>  Children are asking:" Mommy, when are we going home?"  They are doing fine but they miss their home, toys, relatives...</FONT>   </STRONG>
<P>
<FONT SIZE="+1">Novi Sad, FR Yugoslavia (Serbia-Montenegro), August 1995<BR>
<BR><I>&copy; 1995, Gordana Todorov</I></FONT>
