<TITLE> "Patriotic" Croatian Press</TITLE>
<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF">
<FONT SIZE="+1">Article about the writing of the <A HREF="http://www.tiac.net/users/wid/" >Croatian media law</a> by an American media expert who was an advisor to the Croatian government.<P>

<h2><A NAME="hrslovo"><IMG ALT="Hrvatsko Slovo" SRC="hrslo.gif" ALIGN=BOTTOM></a></h2>

<a href="cromedia.html#hrslovo">Hrvatsko Slovo</a> [Croatian Voice] is a weekly for culture from Zagreb.  It was founded as a a patriotic counterpart to the weekly publication of Matica Hrvatska, Vijenac [Wreath].<p>

<ul>
<li><A HREF = "hrslovo1.html"> Victory over Fascism </A> 5/5/95</LI>
<LI><A HREF = "hrslovo2.html"> Spiritual Croatia; A Return </A> 5/5/95</LI>
<LI><A HREF = "hrslovo3.html"> Bihac: a Bulwark of Croatian Glory and Suffering </A>: A Croatian version of the recent history of the Bihac region - Croatian fascist patriots fight Serb bolshevik-chetnik hordes,  9/8/95
<LI><A HREF = "hrslovo6.html">Democracy is not a Diktat to the Judicial System of an Independent State</A>: why the Hague Tribunal has no right to try Croatian soldiers and officers,  3/8/96<IMG SRC="star.gif" ALIGN="MIDDLE">
<LI><A HREF = "hrslovo4.html"> Arson, Mistreatment and a Lie</A>: internal enemies, Bosniak-Croat Federation and Serbs commit suicide,  3/15/96
<LI><A HREF = "hrslovo5.html"> Our Existence is a Crime</A>: why do Muslims hate Croats?,  3/22/96<IMG SRC="star.gif" ALIGN="MIDDLE">
<LI><A HREF = "hrslovo5.html#disinfection"> Disinfection </A>: Croatian independent media pollute Croatian space with lies,  3/22/96<IMG SRC="star.gif" ALIGN="MIDDLE">
</ul>
<p>

<h2><A NAME="slodal"><IMG ALT="Slobodna Dalmacija" SRC="slodal/slodal.gif" ALIGN=BOTTOM></a></h2>  <A HREF="SD.html">Slobodna Dalmacija</a><p>

<ul>
<li><A HREF = "slodal/slodal1.html">HDZ Donates Blood </A> 5/6/95</LI>
<LI>Press Conference at the U.N. Headquarters in Zagreb:<A HREF = "slodal/slodal2.html">Accusations From a Secret Document  </A> 5/6/95</LI>
<LI>Foreign Media and the Freedom of Press in Croatia:<A HREF = "slodal/slodal3.html">Envious Hissings  </A> 9/14/95
<LI><A HREF = "slodal/slodal4.html">Stipe Mesic Evicted </A>: defector from the ruling party evicted from his apartment, 9/14/95
<li><A HREF="slodal/slodal6.html">Herceg-Bosna is Ready for the Hague</a>, Smiljko Sagolj explains the reasons for the indictments against Tihomir Blaskic and Dario Kordic, 11/24/95</LI>
