<HR>
<IMG SRC="pictures/refpic3c.gif"  WIDTH=341 HIGHT=520 ALIGN="RIGHT">
<P>

<STRONG><FONT SIZE="+2">From Petrovac [a town in western Bosnia] to Novi Sad, I rode like this; a total of 750km.  The tractor was full of old women, four or five of them, including my 83-year-old mother.  I came back from the front to take care of her.<P>

I had to ride on the fender to direct a young fellow, an unexperienced driver.  it was like being a cowboy on a mechanical horse.</FONT>
</STRONG>
<P>
<FONT SIZE="+1">Novi Sad, FR Yugoslavia (Serbia-Montenegro), August 1995<BR>
<BR><I>&copy; 1995, Gordana Todorov</I></FONT><P>

<IMG SRC="pictures/refpic2d.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM" WIDTH=543 HIGHT=364><P>
 

