<h1><BR>NORTHEASTERN UNIVERSITY<BR> HUSKY HOCKEY </h1>

<hr align="right" width="100%">
<BR CLEAR="left">


<h2>1996-97 WOMEN'S SCHEDULE:   (home, <font color = "black">away</font>)  </h2>

