<H2> <IMG SRC="gifs/ball2.blue.gif"> My undergrad days : </H2> <P>

I went to the Birla Institute of Technology, Mesra, Ranchi, India for my 
bachelors degree in Electronics and Communication Engg. BIT has a 780 acre 
campus located at the confluence of two seasonal rivers, Jumar and Suvernrekha.
Its almost 16 kilometers away from the nearest town Ranchi and with 
woods occupying most of the 780 acres, its "nature at its very best" . . . 
